## Performance

- **USB Detection**: < 1 second
- **Token Creation**: < 5 seconds
- **Backup/Restore**: 1-10 seconds  
- **Memory Usage**: < 100MB peak

## Requirements

- Python 3.8 or higher
- Windows, Linux, or macOS
- Two USB drives for dual storage setup

